WEBVTT

00:00:00.653 --> 00:00:02.160
MISPAR SHALOSH.

00:00:02.020 --> 00:00:02.959
TODA.

00:00:02.160 --> 00:00:03.886
ANA, HAMSHIKHI ET SIPUREKH.

00:00:03.606 --> 00:00:04.781
TODA RABA.

00:00:04.888 --> 00:00:07.649
ANI R-, ikh hob gevolt aykh dertseyln

00:00:07.673 --> 00:00:11.981
az s'iz bashert tsu blaybn lebn, tsu shisn oder tsu blaybn lebn.

00:00:11.981 --> 00:00:15.581
vel ikh aykh a bisl, vos ikh vil aykh dertseyln fun mayn bruder.

00:00:16.059 --> 00:00:19.547
mayn bruder iz s'ershte, iz, hot men genemen

00:00:19.603 --> 00:00:21.937
fun dem gantsn shtot BALTA,

00:00:21.937 --> 00:00:25.363
hot men gedarft tsunoyfnemen tsvey hundert

00:00:25.363 --> 00:00:26.904
m-, yinglekh

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:31.663
oyf, oyf tsu derhargenen. dos ven ⟨v-⟩ zey hobn shoyn gedarft bafrayen.

00:00:31.737 --> 00:00:34.830
⟨h⟩o- iz geven eyner vos hot geheysn Hofman,

00:00:34.830 --> 00:00:36.506
dos gedenk ikh genoy,

00:00:36.529 --> 00:00:39.369
un er hot bakumen dem bafel fun di daytshn,

00:00:39.369 --> 00:00:41.011
fun di esesovtses,

00:00:41.018 --> 00:00:44.238
tsunoyfnemen di mener. tomer nemt er nisht tsunoyf,

00:00:44.238 --> 00:00:45.849
vet men im derhargenen.

00:00:46.722 --> 00:00:50.869
in der ⟨s-⟩ in der grupe fun di tsvey hundert yinglekh

00:00:50.869 --> 00:00:52.284
iz arayngefaln

00:00:52.510 --> 00:00:53.685
mayn bruder

00:00:55.902 --> 00:00:57.761
un mayn shvesterkind

00:01:00.289 --> 00:01:02.544
un nokh, tsvey mentshn,

00:01:03.208 --> 00:01:05.463
vos zey, zey zenen,

00:01:05.554 --> 00:01:07.067
m'hot zey genemen...

00:01:07.157 --> 00:01:09.243
di stants-, BALTA,

00:01:09.486 --> 00:01:13.732
di statsyon fun BALTA iz a dray kilometer fun der shtot.

00:01:14.076 --> 00:01:16.213
m'hot zey genemen in yenem rayon,

00:01:16.641 --> 00:01:18.677
in a goyisher shtub,

00:01:20.353 --> 00:01:24.673
un m'hot zey arayngetribn ahin tsu, un m'hot aroyfgeleygt

00:01:25.095 --> 00:01:27.249
a b- a fas mit benzin,

00:01:27.492 --> 00:01:30.686
un m'hot di ale khevre ongetsunen.

00:01:31.879 --> 00:01:35.079
un s'iz nor geblibn dray mentshn:

00:01:35.389 --> 00:01:37.104
⟨⟩, tsvey yinglekh,

00:01:37.684 --> 00:01:40.158
dos iz mayn bruder mit mayn kuzin,

00:01:40.435 --> 00:01:42.853
eyne⟨n⟩ hot men geshosn, hot er...

00:01:42.853 --> 00:01:44.866
⟨Farkash⟩ hot er geheysn....

00:01:44.991 --> 00:01:48.967
hot er nor gegreykht biz tsu undzer shtub un dortn iz er oysgegangen.

00:01:49.176 --> 00:01:50.924
er hot nisht, di,

00:01:50.924 --> 00:01:53.135
di ranes vos er hot bakumen...

00:01:53.175 --> 00:01:58.535
undzere zenen, undzer, mayn bruder mit mayn kuzin, iz gikher gelofn

00:01:58.677 --> 00:02:00.836
tsishn f- tsishn felder,

00:02:00.836 --> 00:02:05.280
vayl es iz nisht geven keyn bafelkerung, biz tsu der stantsye.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.798
hobn zey gedarft, durkh di

00:02:07.798 --> 00:02:11.381
v-, durkh di,..., ⟨⟩,

00:02:10.692 --> 00:02:11.614
felder?

00:02:11.381 --> 00:02:12.713
felder l- loyfn,

00:02:12.713 --> 00:02:15.086
un er iz arayngekumen koym lebndik.

00:02:15.147 --> 00:02:17.716
un mir hobn im gegebn gikh a bahalt un dos,

00:02:17.716 --> 00:02:19.616
di neshome hot getsitert. zogt er,

00:02:19.616 --> 00:02:21.131
"ikh bin antlofn

00:02:21.289 --> 00:02:22.560
nisht derfar.

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:25.656
kh'hob shoyn gezen der toyt, ken mir gornisht helfn,

00:02:25.656 --> 00:02:28.373
nor ikh hob aykh nisht gevolt makhn keyn tsores."

00:02:28.373 --> 00:02:30.212
dos iz geven zayne verter.

00:02:30.756 --> 00:02:33.230
hobn mir ge⟨r⟩- iz dort geven a boydem.

00:02:33.591 --> 00:02:35.812
iz er aroyf oyfn goyishn boydem,

00:02:35.886 --> 00:02:37.939
zikh bahaltn vayl er hot moyre gehat

00:02:38.046 --> 00:02:40.942
az, ⟨m'vet, ot dos UNK⟩...

00:02:41.758 --> 00:02:47.785
iz men gegangen, m'hot, ge- m'hot, emetser gezogt,

00:02:47.785 --> 00:02:51.472
un s'iz gekumen di daytshn. m'hot im aropgenemen. m'hot im gut geshlogn,

00:02:51.478 --> 00:02:53.329
nor m'hot im nisht geshosn.

00:02:53.329 --> 00:02:54.831
m'hot im nisht geshosn.

00:02:54.972 --> 00:02:57.339
fun dem toyt iz er vider a mol aroys.

00:02:57.339 --> 00:03:01.311
er iz vider a mol ⟨n-⟩ aroys. dos ba- a bashertung vos ikh vil aykh dertseyln.

00:03:01.941 --> 00:03:03.707
nor ⟨s-⟩ fun dem toyt

00:03:04.219 --> 00:03:06.575
hot, iz er, iz er shoyn nisht aroys.

00:03:06.632 --> 00:03:09.953
do iz shoyn geven, az s'iz bashert tsu shisn,

00:03:09.953 --> 00:03:11.507
hot men im derharget.

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:14.136
kh'hob nokh gevolt aykh dertseyln,

00:03:14.293 --> 00:03:16.025
ven m'hot undz getribn

00:03:16.757 --> 00:03:18.911
iz der,

00:03:19.170 --> 00:03:23.062
di, mayn, mayn, t- mayn, mayn tate's shvester,

00:03:23.187 --> 00:03:24.531
dray mentshn,

00:03:24.553 --> 00:03:26.351
vos kh'hob aykh gezogt,

00:03:26.351 --> 00:03:28.513
m-, nokh a shvester,

00:03:29.447 --> 00:03:31.550
Ester-Rivke mit HILDA,

00:03:32.147 --> 00:03:34.031
un ba- mayn babe

00:03:34.662 --> 00:03:38.227
iz oykh geblibn in, in OBODIVKA. azoy iz geven,

00:03:38.227 --> 00:03:40.460
m'iz gekumen aroysnemen di mentshn.

00:03:41.901 --> 00:03:46.985
 m'hot aroysgerufn di mentshn. m'hot, un m'hot zey nisht geshosn. m'hot zey dortn epes

00:03:46.985 --> 00:03:48.218
farnemen.

00:03:48.218 --> 00:03:51.567
er hot nisht uspeyet tsu shisn dem, ir zun,

00:03:51.567 --> 00:03:54.663
Yosl, der, ir zun. hot zi gemeynt az

00:03:54.663 --> 00:03:55.878
me shist im,

00:03:55.878 --> 00:04:00.637
⟨me d-⟩ me shist im. iz zi geblibn oyfn plats. azoy ⟨m'hot⟩, m'hot aroysgenemen dem zun,

00:04:00.637 --> 00:04:03.000
azoy iz di babe zikh ge- geendikt.

00:04:03.147 --> 00:04:05.267
un m'hot zi bagrobn oyf a feld,

00:04:05.357 --> 00:04:07.140
 un me veyst nisht vu.

00:04:07.348 --> 00:04:10.070
un, kartofl iz gevaksn nokh dem,

00:04:10.070 --> 00:04:13.142
vayl, s'iz oykh geven OBODIVKA der kolkhoz,

00:04:13.142 --> 00:04:14.700
oyfn feld dortn.

00:04:14.790 --> 00:04:16.921
er hot genemen der,

00:04:16.921 --> 00:04:21.568
der zun. zi hot gevolt a kadesh, vayl zi iz geven shtark,...

00:04:21.658 --> 00:04:23.477
hot zi gehat dem kadesh.

00:04:23.477 --> 00:04:24.984
iz ⟨zi⟩ geblibn dort.

00:04:24.984 --> 00:04:26.850
dos hob ikh aykh fargesn

00:04:26.957 --> 00:04:29.820
tsu zogn ir toyt, der, babe's.

00:04:31.125 --> 00:04:35.304
un mir zenen shoyn vayter,... vu haltn mir? in,...

00:04:35.631 --> 00:04:38.375
az ir ⟨zolt⟩ geblibn lebn zelbshtendik...

00:04:37.167 --> 00:04:40.468
yo, un ikh bin, ikh hob gearbet.

00:04:40.677 --> 00:04:43.911
un m'hot mikh gerufn, "kum, vos zitsstu in shtub?"

00:04:44.271 --> 00:04:51.605
di mame, danken got, iz a baleboste... ikh veys, azoy iz... tsufridn iz zi nisht geven, vayl s'iz nisht geven der tate,

00:04:51.915 --> 00:04:55.156
nor tsulib mir; ikh hob shtark gevolt, ⟨s'zol z-⟩

00:04:55.156 --> 00:04:56.710
s'zol zayn a shtub,

00:04:56.710 --> 00:04:59.165
vayl ikh hob gevust, ikh hob khasene,

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:02.878
un ikh hob nisht gevolt, zi zol zayn bay mir a dinst.

00:05:02.952 --> 00:05:05.398
kh'hob gevolt, zi zol nokh makhn a shtikl lebn,

00:05:05.398 --> 00:05:07.046
bay etlekhe un draysik yor!

00:05:08.048 --> 00:05:13.099
un ikh bin gega- un di, m- di khavertes, vos ikh hob ge- "kum aroys!"

00:05:13.099 --> 00:05:15.242
un bin gegangen, dos ershte mol

00:05:15.242 --> 00:05:19.165
vos ikh bin gegangen. ikh fleg nisht azoy geyn. ikh fleg mikh hitn. ikh bin geven

00:05:19.165 --> 00:05:23.820
a ⟨ANSTÄNDIG⟩ kind. ikh hob moyre gehat far di shkotsim. kh'hob m- moyre gehat...

00:05:24.298 --> 00:05:28.139
un gey arayn in, in, es iz geven a yidisher,

00:05:28.433 --> 00:05:30.682
 me fleg tantsn dortn.

00:05:30.682 --> 00:05:35.733
es fleg zikh tsunoyfkumen yidishe bokhurim, yidishe meydelekh.

00:05:35.976 --> 00:05:39.463
m'hot ⟨zikh⟩ dokh gemuzt ergets, tsunoyfkumen.

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.786
un azoy ikh bin arayngekumen,

00:05:41.786 --> 00:05:44.238
azoy vi s'iz geven a basherte zakh,

00:05:44.413 --> 00:05:49.254
ikh bin geshtanen azoy. ikh gib a kuk. ikh heyb oyf dem kop, gib a kuk, er kukt oyf m-...

00:05:49.254 --> 00:05:52.220
s'iz azoy vi a magnet. s'iz geven epes aza...

00:05:52.530 --> 00:05:55.961
er hot gegebn a kuk un ikh hob gegebn a kuk: er kukt oyf mir,

00:05:55.961 --> 00:05:58.531
⟨un⟩ er iz mikh shoyn gekumen tsunemen tantsn,

00:05:59.415 --> 00:06:01.518
un azoy hob ikh mikh bakant mit im.

00:06:02.014 --> 00:06:05.484
vi mir ⟨z-⟩ hobn zikh shoyn gezen, hobn mir zikh shoyn umedum...

00:06:05.811 --> 00:06:10.547
un nokh dem, ikh fle-, flegn mir zikh shabes bagegenen un aldings.

00:06:10.587 --> 00:06:13.967
kh'hob gevust, un dervayl, ikh tor gornisht trakhtn

00:06:13.967 --> 00:06:16.014
vayl er hot gedarft geyn in der,

00:06:16.797 --> 00:06:20.371
in der TSAVA. er iz geven far ⟨der⟩...

00:06:21.370 --> 00:06:27.000
un, trakht ikh, "ikh ⟨t-⟩ ikh vil nokh nisht khasene hobn, loz zayn..."

00:06:28.373 --> 00:06:31.371
eyn nokh zakh vil ikh aykh far dem...

00:06:31.849 --> 00:06:35.955
az ikh bin geven farshrib- s'e- az ikh hob shoyn gezen

00:06:35.955 --> 00:06:38.486
az mayn mame iz azoy un ales,

00:06:38.486 --> 00:06:39.848
hob ikh getrakht,

00:06:39.848 --> 00:06:41.321
⟨O⟩ ⟨s'⟩iz geven a rebe,

00:06:41.321 --> 00:06:42.963
vos hot farshribn

00:06:43.020 --> 00:06:44.476
yesoymes

00:06:44.476 --> 00:06:45.883
keyn Erets-Yisroel.

00:06:46.142 --> 00:06:48.515
un ikh bin dokh geven a tsienistke.

00:06:49.146 --> 00:06:51.252
azoy ikh hob dos gehert,

00:06:51.252 --> 00:06:52.599
bin ikh gegangen,

00:06:52.740 --> 00:06:56.981
un mayn kuzin, der vos azoy ⟨iz⟩ geblibn lebn, un nokh a kuzin funem,

00:06:56.981 --> 00:06:59.112
mayn mame's bruder's a zun,

00:06:59.170 --> 00:07:02.390
un mir zenen zikh gegangen farshraybn: mir forn keyn

00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:03.787
ERETS-YISRAEL,

00:07:04.148 --> 00:07:06.015
in, kibuts,

00:07:07.523 --> 00:07:11.044
un der rebe iz geven zeyer tsufridn. s'iz geven a...

00:07:12.484 --> 00:07:14.115
geyendik aheym

00:07:14.290 --> 00:07:15.870
fun dem rebe,

00:07:16.770 --> 00:07:20.611
gib ikh mikh a, a batrakht, un zets mikh nider un heyb on veynen.

00:07:21.917 --> 00:07:24.012
di milkhome bin ikh aroys.

00:07:24.403 --> 00:07:26.085
ikh bin geblibn ⟨mit⟩ der mame.

00:07:32.612 --> 00:07:34.241
UNK

00:07:40.623 --> 00:07:42.572
itster zol ikh zi iberlozn?

00:07:43.795 --> 00:07:48.013
fun ergets nisht! vos vet zayn mit der mame vet zayn mit mir oykh.

00:07:48.797 --> 00:07:51.920
dos hob ikh aykh fargesn dos tsu dertseyln.

00:07:52.573 --> 00:07:54.555
kh'hob gezogt ⟨a meydl⟩,

00:07:54.555 --> 00:07:55.917
"kh'⟨vel⟩ zi iberlozn?"

00:07:55.917 --> 00:07:59.462
ikh hob nisht moyre gehat tsu forn, vayl ikh bin geven a...

00:08:00.493 --> 00:08:03.244
mir hobn gevust khalutskes, mir hobn geto-...

00:08:03.244 --> 00:08:05.553
azoy se darf zayn a khalutske, un,

00:08:05.553 --> 00:08:08.554
un ales, az ikh darf zayn ATSMAIT.

00:08:08.593 --> 00:08:14.142
s'iz nishto keyn kinder, gesheftn. un az kh'hob mikh shoyn bagegnt mit im

00:08:14.142 --> 00:08:18.088
un ikh hob gearbet, ikh bin bl⟨ay⟩ter geblibn, lernen,

00:08:18.482 --> 00:08:23.319
un er hot gezogt tsu mir, "veyst vos, Roze? ikh gey avek in der TSAVA,

00:08:23.443 --> 00:08:26.997
un du bist a meydl, du kenst khasene hobn.

00:08:27.088 --> 00:08:29.233
 du

00:08:29.233 --> 00:08:31.469
kenst oyf mir nisht vartn dray yor."

00:08:31.965 --> 00:08:35.756
un nokh dem hobn mir gezen az mir hobn zikh shoyn azoy lib,

00:08:35.756 --> 00:08:37.763
iz er gekumen, er hot gezogt azoy: "kuk,

00:08:37.821 --> 00:08:39.418
az du host mikh lib,

00:08:40.116 --> 00:08:45.865
un azoy, iz, az du vilst vartn dray yor, kum ikh tsu- fun der, TSAVA,

00:08:45.865 --> 00:08:47.539
un mir hobn khasene."

00:08:48.250 --> 00:08:49.668
zog ikh, "nu, gut.

00:08:49.668 --> 00:08:53.005
ikh vel mikh nisht khasene hobn. ikh lern nokh in dervayl.

00:08:53.005 --> 00:08:54.099
ikh arbet."

00:08:54.443 --> 00:08:57.744
un mir hobn ge- opgeredt tsishn zikh,

00:08:57.852 --> 00:09:02.573
dos iz geven in, mir hobn zikh bagegnt in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:09:02.573 --> 00:09:04.868
in nayn un fertsikstn yor iz er gegangen

00:09:04.868 --> 00:09:09.590
in der, in der TSAVA, un ikh hob gev- un ikh hob gevart.

00:09:10.305 --> 00:09:11.801
kh'hob gevart

00:09:11.875 --> 00:09:13.472
oyf im dray yor.

00:09:13.714 --> 00:09:14.816
dray yor

00:09:14.816 --> 00:09:16.273
hob ikh gevart oyf im.

00:09:16.954 --> 00:09:22.196
vayl er iz geven shtark a ⟨,⟩ feiker, er iz geven a mentsh,

00:09:22.202 --> 00:09:24.257
hot men im nokh tsen khadoshim

00:09:24.257 --> 00:09:26.887
in der TSAVA, me zol aheymlozn

00:09:27.315 --> 00:09:33.401
in, in, in KHOFESH, ⟨in...in⟩ fray bakumen oyf tsvey vokhn, darf men zayn,

00:09:33.475 --> 00:09:35.483
fardinen shtark gut.

00:09:35.601 --> 00:09:38.801
un er hot dos, vayl er iz geven,

00:09:38.824 --> 00:09:42.415
⟨, a⟩ ofitser un er hot durkhgefirt

00:09:42.415 --> 00:09:43.762
zeyer a,

00:09:43.937 --> 00:09:47.898
a sheyne arbet. zey hobn bakumen s'ershte plats UNK.

00:09:48.055 --> 00:09:51.407
hobn zey im gegebn aheymforn. az er iz gekumen aheym,

00:09:51.885 --> 00:09:54.236
hot er, hot di mame gezogt,

00:09:54.236 --> 00:09:56.463
vayl mir hobn zikh gefirt yidish,

00:09:56.463 --> 00:09:58.561
me zol makhn tnoim.

00:09:58.561 --> 00:10:00.210
un mir hobn gemakht tnoim

00:10:00.210 --> 00:10:01.548
vi bay di

00:10:01.588 --> 00:10:03.674
NAS-, AMITI.

00:10:04.035 --> 00:10:06.256
mir hobn gebrokhn a teler

00:10:06.634 --> 00:10:09.125
un mir hobn gemakht, tnoim,

00:10:09.165 --> 00:10:14.053
un er iz avekgeforn, un ikh bin mir geblibn vartn. mir hobn geshribn briv.

00:10:14.498 --> 00:10:20.316
ikh hob, ge- gehat, kh'hob bakumen, fun der arbet,

00:10:20.316 --> 00:10:21.683
 fray,

00:10:21.683 --> 00:10:23.182
 tsvey vokhn.

00:10:23.391 --> 00:10:26.214
iz geven dortn a familye zayne.

00:10:26.214 --> 00:10:30.275
bin ikh hingeforn vayl er hot UNK. kh'bin geven dortn

00:10:30.275 --> 00:10:33.932
un er fleg, im fleg men oplozn, mir flegn dos o.

00:10:34.275 --> 00:10:35.968
un,

00:10:35.968 --> 00:10:37.340
nokh dem

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:41.881
hot men im geshikt in der, akademye,

00:10:42.527 --> 00:10:46.505
 lernen, ⟨,⟩ ofi- er iz geven ⟨a⟩ ofitsir UNK.

00:10:46.898 --> 00:10:51.746
hot er gedarft bakumen a shtub un ales. m'hot im gedarft ibershraybn

00:10:51.746 --> 00:10:53.636
a shtub vayl,

00:10:53.636 --> 00:10:56.949
vayl azoy er iz geven a bokher hot er nisht gekent dos bakumen.

00:10:57.107 --> 00:11:00.428
hot er mir gegebn a telegram. er hot gezogt dortn,

00:11:00.428 --> 00:11:03.699
s'iz bay im nisht keyn BEAYA; er hot a kale.

00:11:04.212 --> 00:11:07.628
un zey hobn ge- ⟨a⟩ sakh hobn gevust, er hot a kale, nor di vo-

00:11:07.628 --> 00:11:09.506
der hoypt hot nisht gevust.

00:11:09.561 --> 00:11:13.330
zogt er, "ikh gib a telegram. morgn kumt mayn k- mayn kale."

00:11:13.330 --> 00:11:14.634
un ikh farshrayb mikh

00:11:15.045 --> 00:11:17.075
un mir,

00:11:17.075 --> 00:11:19.173
un s'i- un mir bakumen...

00:11:19.500 --> 00:11:22.666
nor vayl di antisemitishe, nokh dem,

00:11:22.666 --> 00:11:24.961
er hot nisht gevust az mir zenen yidn.

00:11:26.149 --> 00:11:31.231
s'ershte hot er gemakht, farn farshraybn in ZAGS... dort farshraybt men in ZAGS...

