00:22:52.742 --> 00:22:54.508
un mir blaybn

00:22:54.514 --> 00:22:55.659
dort.

00:22:55.659 --> 00:22:56.945
me lozt nisht aroys.

00:22:56.945 --> 00:22:58.247
mir hobn di

00:22:58.247 --> 00:22:59.402
erloybenish

00:23:00.184 --> 00:23:02.743
un mir, me lozt undz nisht aroys.

00:23:03.728 --> 00:23:07.603
un s'iz gevorn opgerisn di diplomatishe,

00:23:09.027 --> 00:23:10.904
diplomatishe

00:23:10.904 --> 00:23:12.898
b- batsiungen mit,

00:23:12.898 --> 00:23:14.857
mit, YISRAEL. er, di

00:23:14.857 --> 00:23:16.935
⟨rus-,⟩ punkt shabes.

00:23:16.992 --> 00:23:18.515
ikh gey in shtot,

00:23:18.515 --> 00:23:26.131
her ikh vi s'- vi s'iz gevorn ibergerisn di dip- diplomatishe batsiungen mit, mit YISRAEL.

00:23:26.712 --> 00:23:29.047
hob ikh mikh shtark tseveynt,

00:23:29.158 --> 00:23:31.661
vayl ikh bin geblibn nisht hin un aher.

00:23:31.661 --> 00:23:34.434
kh'hob shoyn ales mir tsugegreyt tsu forn.

00:23:35.301 --> 00:23:40.875
un ikh bin shoyn geven greyt aldings. kh'hob gevart, haynt-morgn darf ikh aroysforn.

00:23:40.875 --> 00:23:43.344
un do zenen mir farblibn

00:23:43.367 --> 00:23:46.061
biz tsun akht un zekhtsikstn yor.

00:23:46.843 --> 00:23:51.481
kh'hob shoyn nokh a mol gekoyft kartoflyes. kh'hob shoyn nokh a mol gekoyft a betl.

00:23:51.481 --> 00:23:55.047
un ikh veyn shoyn vayter un vart shoyn di gute minut,

00:23:55.047 --> 00:23:56.993
az me zol undz aroyslozn.

00:23:57.289 --> 00:23:59.072
ikh hob in dervayl,

00:23:59.179 --> 00:24:04.083
 ge- ⟨ikh, hob ikh⟩, ge- d- ikh hob opgearbet. ikh hob avekgevarfn di arbet

00:24:04.140 --> 00:24:06.660
vayl kh'hob geboyrn a kind, un nokh dem

00:24:06.660 --> 00:24:07.816
nokh a mol,

00:24:07.816 --> 00:24:12.047
ot dos tsveyte kind. hob ikh in dervayl mir gelernt biblyoteker.

00:24:12.047 --> 00:24:14.911
hob ikh gearbet biblyoteker in a LESESAAL.

00:24:14.911 --> 00:24:16.258
ikh gey oyf der nakht

00:24:16.258 --> 00:24:18.333
aheym fun der arbet. kh'hob gearbet

00:24:18.333 --> 00:24:20.598
fun tsen, halb tsen biz tsen,

00:24:20.695 --> 00:24:23.367
un kum, oyfn veg, gib a kuk: mayn man,

00:24:23.367 --> 00:24:24.374
der invalid,

00:24:24.455 --> 00:24:25.564
mit dem shtekn,

00:24:25.564 --> 00:24:26.991
bay nakht dreyt er zikh arum.

00:24:26.991 --> 00:24:28.871
mir hobn bakumen a tsetl fun der

00:24:28.871 --> 00:24:30.679
⟨AVIR⟩, fun der N.K.V.D.,

00:24:30.702 --> 00:24:33.666
az in dray teg arum darfn mir zikh yaven.

00:24:33.823 --> 00:24:36.060
un mir veysn nisht vos iz geshen.

00:24:36.060 --> 00:24:38.718
dray nekht un dray sh-, teg nisht geshlofn,

00:24:38.718 --> 00:24:40.990
vayl mir veysn nisht vos me ruft undz aroys.

00:24:40.990 --> 00:24:43.229
er zogt, "mistam shikt men undz aroys."

00:24:43.229 --> 00:24:45.275
derfar, vayl mir hobn ayngegebn,

00:24:45.275 --> 00:24:47.427
un s'iz itstert aza gesheft...

00:24:47.427 --> 00:24:50.521
iz hot men gezogt, me shikt aroys keyn Sibir oder vu.

00:24:50.521 --> 00:24:53.052
hobn, zenen mir geven di gantse nakht, vos ⟨mir z-⟩...

00:24:53.052 --> 00:24:54.129
biz dray teg.

00:24:54.129 --> 00:24:56.177
ongekumen in dray teg ahin tsu,

00:24:56.723 --> 00:25:00.045
un me git undz a zog di psure un mir gleybn shoyn nisht!

00:25:00.045 --> 00:25:04.243
az "ir darft zikh, ir hot ot di ⟨bavilungung⟩ keyn IZRAIL',

00:25:04.333 --> 00:25:07.181
nor mir veysn nokh nisht, azoy ts-, azoy ir zolt

00:25:07.181 --> 00:25:10.486
⟨z- z-⟩ ver se darf ⟨aykh⟩ aroyslozn, azoy,

00:25:10.510 --> 00:25:14.877
nor ir darft aleyn... ir bak- ikh hob ag-, ir darft zikh oprekhenen.

00:25:14.877 --> 00:25:18.649
ir darft fo- durkhforn dray,

00:25:18.649 --> 00:25:20.781
 dray, ⟨⟩, lender.

00:25:21.208 --> 00:25:24.951
un ikh veys nisht ver se darf aykh gebn di, di ⟨bavilungung⟩."

00:25:24.951 --> 00:25:30.263
nor, a glik, mir hobn geho- gehert KOL YISRAEL

00:25:30.263 --> 00:25:32.360
un mir hobn gehert az in

00:25:32.360 --> 00:25:34.477
der, ⟨ge-⟩

00:25:34.477 --> 00:25:36.255
holandish, f-,

00:25:36.615 --> 00:25:37.604
Holand,

00:25:37.847 --> 00:25:41.362
iz do a mentsh, vos er,

00:25:41.362 --> 00:25:45.216
hot, undzer, TAFKID. er hot ⟨ot⟩ dortn undzer...

00:25:45.829 --> 00:25:51.746
un mir zenen nisht farshlofene mentshn, un mir forn keyn Moskve, bakumen di...

00:25:51.955 --> 00:25:56.319
do hot men shoyn tsugenemen undzere pasportn, un mir zenen shoyn nisht aher, nisht ahin.

00:25:56.865 --> 00:26:03.339
un mir kumen on ahin tsu, un keyner veys gornisht. mir hobn nor funem KOL-YISRAEL gevust vu zey gefinen zikh.

00:26:03.666 --> 00:26:09.242
nor ⟨m-,⟩ zenen mir ongekumen. iz geven dortn a rusishe N.K.V.D. m'hot nisht gekent ahin tsugeyn.

00:26:09.242 --> 00:26:11.943
fregt men, "vos darft ir hobn?" un do hobn mir moyre tsu zogn,

00:26:11.943 --> 00:26:13.498
vos mir darfn hobn.

00:26:13.521 --> 00:26:17.666
nor m'hot shoyn gez-, gemuzt zogn, un mir kumen ahin tsu.

00:26:18.297 --> 00:26:24.653
nu, hot men undz oyfgenemen di papirn, un m'hot undz gezogt az zey iz do eyner a fartreter.

00:26:24.653 --> 00:26:28.162
shlofn hobn mir nisht vu. mir kenen nisht geyn in keyn shum...

00:26:28.270 --> 00:26:30.508
vayl mir zenen shoyn nisht keyn...

00:26:30.919 --> 00:26:36.110
hobn mir gedarft geyn tsu der ⟨AUSTRishe⟩, ⟨AUSTRIYA⟩ zenen mir durkhgeforn, un VENGRIYA.

00:26:36.707 --> 00:26:37.933
Budapest.

00:26:38.783 --> 00:26:40.076
un

00:26:40.842 --> 00:26:42.878
mir hobn dos durkhgegangen,

00:26:42.934 --> 00:26:45.526
un danken got, mir kumen aheym,

00:26:46.225 --> 00:26:48.179
un mir farpakn zikh,

00:26:48.179 --> 00:26:50.252
un mir zenen durkhgegangen di ale...

00:26:51.051 --> 00:26:55.213
ikh mit im, vos er iz gevorn invalid, di tsveyte grupe,

00:26:55.523 --> 00:26:57.559
hot er f- hot er bakumen

00:26:58.054 --> 00:27:01.946
vaser oyf kashe. finef un draysik, rubl a khoydesh.

00:27:02.053 --> 00:27:04.696
finef rubl hot men gegebn far tsvey kinder,

00:27:04.838 --> 00:27:06.496
nor ikh hob gearbet.

00:27:06.677 --> 00:27:09.725
un mir hobn, mir zenen geven mentshn...

00:27:09.782 --> 00:27:12.526
nor mir hobn zikh gekent oys⟨UNK⟩n undzer lebn.

00:27:14.018 --> 00:27:15.702
un,

00:27:15.702 --> 00:27:19.789
in Moskve, ⟨f- vi m'iz⟩ tsurikgekumen fun Moskve, hobn mir zikh farpakt.

00:27:20.177 --> 00:27:22.637
mir hobn nisht ge- er hot gezogt, keynem nisht zogn

00:27:22.637 --> 00:27:24.322
un keynem nisht redn.

00:27:24.413 --> 00:27:29.782
un azoy zol m- es tor keyner nisht visn. afile mir ⟨veln⟩ forn keyn Moskve, hot men undz gezogt,

00:27:29.782 --> 00:27:31.207
tor keyner nisht visn.

00:27:31.888 --> 00:27:35.999
un mir zenen ongekumen, yo, aroysforndik,

00:27:36.867 --> 00:27:38.990
hobn mir s'ershte avekgezetst di kinder,

00:27:38.990 --> 00:27:41.770
undzere kinder fregn, "libe kinder..."

00:27:41.770 --> 00:27:42.280
er.

00:27:42.280 --> 00:27:43.239
zogt er,

00:27:43.245 --> 00:27:45.517
"⟨ir n-⟩ zey muzn veysn ales."

00:27:45.777 --> 00:27:51.207
fun im hot men nisht gevust, er iz, er iz krank. di muter mitn, d- di m- zayn mame mitn tate

00:27:51.207 --> 00:27:53.144
hot keyner nisht gevust

00:27:53.370 --> 00:27:56.013
vos mit, az er iz gezunt,

00:27:56.020 --> 00:27:57.634
vos er iz glaykh.

00:27:57.690 --> 00:28:01.008
m'hot im gezen a kripl. m'hot zikh getseylemt

00:28:01.521 --> 00:28:02.758
un ales.

00:28:02.758 --> 00:28:04.822
vos zhe, bet ir, iz forgekumen?

00:28:04.845 --> 00:28:07.994
mir zenen ongek- yo, mir zenen aroysgeforn

00:28:09.958 --> 00:28:12.989
un in Budapest hot men undz gevart,

00:28:13.300 --> 00:28:18.005
m- arayngegebn di vagonen, in a kupe. m'hot gezogt, me zol nisht redn gornisht,

00:28:18.005 --> 00:28:19.301
me zol shvaygn.

00:28:19.425 --> 00:28:21.933
s'hot getsitert hent un fis oyf undz.

00:28:22.328 --> 00:28:26.068
mir geyen nor arop in Budapest, shteyt a, shteyt eyner,

00:28:27.357 --> 00:28:31.417
hobn mir zikh shtark ibergeshrokn, un zogt, "ver zent ir?"

00:28:31.474 --> 00:28:34.235
⟨a⟩zoy un azoy. ⟨⟩, hot undz gevart oyf undz.

00:28:34.326 --> 00:28:35.698
hobn mir getrakht, ot hostu

00:28:35.698 --> 00:28:37.880
dos iz shoyn mistam a N.K.V.D.

00:28:37.903 --> 00:28:40.051
un dos iz geven a,

00:28:40.051 --> 00:28:41.240
geshikt

00:28:41.240 --> 00:28:42.490
fun, fun IZRAIL'.

00:28:42.490 --> 00:28:43.866
zey hobn shoyn gevust

00:28:43.866 --> 00:28:47.106
az mir darfn durkhforn, hobn zey gehat

00:28:47.106 --> 00:28:49.064
TAYNYY agentn.

00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:55.818
un shtelt aykh for undzer, MATSAV: me nemt undz arop, me nemt tsu dem bagazh,

00:28:55.993 --> 00:28:57.428
un me firt undz.

00:28:57.428 --> 00:28:59.481
nor m'hot undz gefirt in a hotel,

00:28:59.773 --> 00:29:02.686
un m'hot undz gegebn a, a K- a K- a shtub.

00:29:04.650 --> 00:29:06.506
un in der shtub

00:29:06.506 --> 00:29:07.423
in hotel,

00:29:07.423 --> 00:29:09.549
hot men gezogt, az m'vet klingen

00:29:09.549 --> 00:29:10.428
ayer...

00:29:10.428 --> 00:29:11.934
vet ir aykh aroplozn

00:29:11.957 --> 00:29:13.385
in-, untn.

00:29:13.425 --> 00:29:14.953
m'vet aykh gebn esn.

00:29:14.967 --> 00:29:18.820
ir zolt visn azoy, nor ir zolt gornisht mit keynem redn UNK.

00:29:19.281 --> 00:29:23.230
mir hobn ibergeshlofn di nakht. in der fri hot er ongeklungen.

00:29:23.415 --> 00:29:26.672
nor m- dos harts iz oysgegangen far shrek.
